- [[HTML 2.0]]: [[RFC 1866]] 5.2.4. Link: LINK
- [[HTML 4]]
-- ''Links in HTML documents'' <IW:HTML4:"struct/links.html">
--- 12.3 Document relationships: the LINK element 
<IW:HTML4:"struct/links.html#edef-LINK">

